select distinct CASE WHEN trim(AK.IndexName) IS NULL THEN trim(AK.IndexType) ||'_'||trim(AK.TableName)||'_'||trim(AK.IndexNumber) ELSE trim(AK.IndexName) END (named INDEX_NAME), trim(AK.ColumnName) (named COLUMN_NAME), AK.ColumnPosition (named "POSITION") from DBC.Indices AK where AK.IndexType ='S' and trim(AK.TableName) = :TABLE and AK.DatabaseName = :SCHEMA order by 1,2,3

select distinct CASE WHEN trim(AK.IndexName) IS NULL THEN trim(AK.IndexType) ||'_'||trim(AK.TableName)||'_'||trim(AK.IndexNumber) ELSE trim(AK.IndexName) END (named INDEX_NAME), trim(AK.ColumnName) (named COLUMN_NAME), AK.ColumnPosition (named "POSITION") from DBC.Indices AK where AK.IndexType ='S' and trim(AK.TableName) = :TABLE and AK.DatabaseName = :SCHEMA order by 1,2,3

select trim(CK.ConstraintName) (named CHECK_NAME), SUBSTRING( CK.ConstraintText FROM INDEX(CK.ConstraintText,'(')+2 FOR CHARACTER_LENGTH(CK.ConstraintText)-INDEX(CK.ConstraintText,'(')-3) (named CHECK_TXT), 1 (named CHECK_STATUS), '' (named CHECK_DESC) from DBC.Table_LevelConstraints CK where TableName = :TABLE and DatabaseName = :SCHEMA

trim(ctvf.FieldName) FK_COLUMN_NAME, trim(ptvf.FieldName) PK_COLUMN_NAME from dbc.ReferencingTbls rt, dbc.TVM ctvm, dbc.dbase cdb, dbc.tvfields ctvf, dbc.TVM ptvm, dbc.dbase pdb, dbc.tvfields ptvf where ctvm.TVMId = rt.ReferencingTblId and ctvm.DatabaseId = cdb.DatabaseId and ctvf.TableId = rt.ReferencingTblId and ctvf.FieldId = rt.ForeignKeyFID and ptvm.TVMId = rt.ReferencedTblId and ptvm.DatabaseId = pdb.DatabaseId and ptvf.TableId = rt.ReferencedTblId and ptvf.FieldId = rt.ParentKeyFID and pdb.DatabaseName = :SCHEMA and ptvm.TVMName = :TABLE
